The paper deals with formal verification of embedded systems, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories of computer science. The use of Isabelle theorem-prover suggests that the paper may belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. The paper also deals with software engineering tools such as Simulink, which suggests that it may belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper's focus on translations and algorithms suggests that it may belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category. The paper deals with embedded systems, which suggests that it may belong to the Embedded Systems (cs.ET) sub-category. Finally, the paper's focus on block diagrams and formal semantics suggests that it may belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
